suspended for a year or two.

153
00:08:29,558 --> 00:08:31,558
I contacted Johns Hopkins
University in America.

154
00:08:31,658 --> 00:08:33,788
How about you study
there for a while?

155
00:08:34,327 --> 00:08:36,898
Aren't medical mistakes
and malpractice issues...

156
00:08:37,398 --> 00:08:39,168
