living the way you did.

200
00:12:48,178 --> 00:12:49,717
I don't intend to kill you.

201
00:12:50,447 --> 00:12:52,347
I won't maim you either.

202
00:12:52,947 --> 00:12:54,918
I'm letting you live
for one reason only.

203
00:12:56,117 --> 00:12:58,658
I just talked to your
father James Lee.

204
00:13:01,898 --> 00:13:04,197
What did you do, you psycho?

205
00:13:05,428 --> 00:13:07,567
I bargained with him.

206
00:13:08,138 --> 00:13:09,168
With Min Seol A's case.

207
00:13:11,437 --> 00:13:14,508
I can't believe that
brat helped me out again.

208
00:13:14,737 --> 00:13:15,878
Shut your mouth!

209
